  [Excerpt] New Delhi, April 21 (PTI)--Around 2,500 civilians 
were killed in various kinds of terrorist-related violence in 
Jammu and Kashmir during the past three years, viz. 1991-93, 
while 73 such deaths were reported from Delhi for the same 
period, the Lok Sabha was told today. [passage omitted] 

