  [Text] The IDF [Israel Defense Forces] foiled an attempt 
by three terrorists to infiltrate the settlement of Neve Deqalim 
in the Qatif Bloc this morning. An IDF force pursued the 
terrorists out of the settlement. One terrorist was 
apprehended, another was shot in the leg and detained after he 
tried to attack a soldier, and the third terrorist managed to 
escape. Our correspondent Moti Amir reports that the IDF lodged 
a complaint with the Palestinian police and is continuing to 
investigate the incident. 

