<H4>    Thai Minister Denies Any Iranian Protest </H4>

<F P=102> BK0806042594 Bangkok BANGKOK POST in English 8 Jun 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> BK0806042594 </F>
<F P=104>  Bangkok BANGKOK POST </F>
