BFN 

  [Excerpt] As a result of two operations, one in Santiago 
and another in Concepcion, Dipolcar [Carabineros Intelligence 
Directorate] agents dismantled a Mapu Lautaro cell and arrested 
two men and one woman allegedly involved in terrorist actions. 
  The arrested people were identified as Daniel Andrade 
Sanchez, 26; Jorge Ruminot Sagredo, 24; and Ruth Tobar Montoya, 
