<H3> <TI>   Egypt Seeks Information on Al-Jihad-al-Tufayli Contacts </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Egypt Seeks Information on Al-Jihad-al-Tufayli Contacts </PHRASE></F></HT>

