<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Egyptian security agencies are trying to gather 
information about meetings between a delegation of Egypt's 
al-Jihad Organization and Shaykh Subhi al-Tufayli, former 
secretary general of Lebanon's Hizballah. These agencies have 
obtained information that several Egyptian "Afghans" [Egyptians 
who fought alongside the Afghan Mujahidin against Soviets], who 
were expelled from Pakistan, have arrived in Lebanon and are now 
under Hizballah's protection. 

</TEXT>

