  [Text] Mohammad Kazem Khonsari, director general of Middle 
East and North African Affairs in the Iranian Foreign Ministry, 
today called on Foreign Minister Faris Buwayz; Shaykh Muhammad 
Mahdi Shams-al-Din, chairman of the Higher Islamic Shiite 
Council; and 'Allamah Sayyid Muhammad Husayn Fadlallah. He said 
that his country supports Lebanon's unity, its people's defense 
