<H3> <TI>   Source Denies Report on Worshiper-Terrorist Clashes </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Source Denies Report on Worshiper-Terrorist Clashes </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC0806065694 Cairo MENA in Arabic 2150 GMT 7 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0806065694 </F>
