  [Text] Gunmen from the subversive organization Hizballah 
kidnapped six Lebanese and a retired Syrian soldier in the 
Ba'labakk area last night. It has been learned that members of 
the so-called Emergency Battalion [katibat al-tawari'] of 
Hizballah kidnapped three of them from their homes after 
mistreating them. They kidnapped the other four in public 
places. Lebanese and Syrian security agencies are holding 
contacts with Hizballah to seek the release of the those 
kidnapped. 

