<H3> <TI>   Sukhoy-35 Flies Aerobatics at Kubinka Show </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Sukhoy-35 Flies Aerobatics at Kubinka Show </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM2305135394 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 
1920 GMT 14 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> PM2305135394 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Russian Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


